E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1716','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-25/ca3e85f61f299f6ba7a76375ab3e1d24.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\">会议现场</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-25/f574c70d0d3ccb85cae8b082e2c894e0.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">获得奖励的学生代表上台领奖</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">23</span>日，全县综合治理出生人口性别比暨打击&ldquo;两非&rdquo;公开处理大会召开。省出生人口性别比综合治理办公室副主任岳勇，市人口计生委主任王勇、副主任罗会牛，熊征宇、余珂等在家的县四大家领导出席会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">岳勇、王勇充分肯定了我县的计划生育工作。岳勇表示，嘉鱼县委、县政府高度重视计划生育工作，主要领导亲自抓，在打击&ldquo;两非&rdquo;上成效比较大，处理也比较到位，在稳定低生育水平方面做了卓有成效的工作。他希望嘉鱼进一步的加大&ldquo;两非&rdquo;案件的查处力度，加大计划生育利益导向的引导和&ldquo;三查四术&rdquo;的排查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">会上，熊征宇要求，全县各级各部门要在思想认识上再提高、再升华，一定要对计生工作有个更加清醒、更加科学、更加全面、更加理性的认识。要正确对待我们自身存在的问题，从中吸取教训，做到人口问题常提、人口工作常抓、人口警钟常鸣，时时刻刻绷紧计划生育的这根弦。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">熊征宇指出，各级各部门要狠抓宣传，营造氛围，要把我们的特色、政策、工作宣传出去，使家喻户晓，全社会明白，打造具有嘉鱼特色的计生宣传品牌，造成强势推力；要狠抓导向、转变观念，要不折不扣的实施好、兑现好县委、县政府出台的各项惠民计生阳光政策，把好事做好，把实事办实，解决计划生育家庭最关心、最直接、最现实的利益问题，从而逐步转变群众的生育观念；要狠抓查处、教育一片，重拳打击&ldquo;两非&rdquo;案件，在严格征收社会抚养费标准的同时抓典型，公开曝光、公开处理，要在社会上造成一定的影响力；要狠抓考评、落实责任，对各镇各项指标完成情况，由县委督办室牵头、组成督办组，巡回督办不间断，督办情况每半个月发一期通报；要狠抓基层、打牢基础，各镇各村要选配年纪较轻、文化程度较高，具备计算机基本知识和操作程序的计生专干；要狠抓队伍、强化管理，要解决&ldquo;两非办&rdquo;的人员编制，增强力量，同时公安、卫生等计生成员单位也要切实负起责任，形成打击&ldquo;两非&rdquo;的合力。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">熊征宇强调，今年是计划生育工作非常年份，前不久，作为出生人口性别比严重偏高的县（市）之一，嘉鱼接受了省委、省政府的约谈，面临这一严峻形势，决定了我们必须要强化措施，狠抓落实，必须做到&ldquo;五个强化&rdquo;，即强化领导、强化责任、强化举措、强化综合治理、强化经费投入。要不断的总结经验、教训、痛下决心，真抓实干，以苦干加实干加巧干的精神，克难攻坚，奋力拼搏，不但要走出困境，而且还要争先进位，打一场计划生育工作的翻身仗。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">县委副书记、县长余珂主持会议，他要求各部门认真贯彻落实会议精神，切实做到主要领导亲自抓、负总责，完善利益导向机制，真正做到主要领导负总责，分管领导负全责、计生专干负专责；要密切配合，整体推进，对于&ldquo;两非&rdquo;案件线索要一查到底，做到一般案例查处到位，典型案例查处及时，公开曝光；按照&ldquo;倒计时&rdquo;的工作日程，&ldquo;倒销号&rdquo;的工作办法，迅速行动起来，大打一场人口和计划生育工作的突击战，攻坚战。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">县委副书记李国光宣读了《关于完善综合治理出生人口性别比工作机制的意见》；县委常委、宣传部长刘合权宣读了《关于全县查处&ldquo;两非&rdquo;典型案件的情况通报》；副县长魏萍通报了全县综合治理出生人口性别比工作情况。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">会议还对在打击&ldquo;两非&rdquo;工作中成绩突出的先进单位和个人进行了颁奖，给享受农村独生女高考加分升学对象颁发了奖学金，相关单位还作了表态发言。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1717','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-26/d43ef745eb156dcebbbabe042e54f52e.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n检查南门大道进展情况<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>日，县人大召开第十七届人大常委会第四次会议，县人大常委会主任李鹏谋，县委常委、常务副县长熊武华，县人大副主任谢望松、秦建平、曾祥坤、李电波、贺隆君、戴书萍参加会议，县法院、县检察院负责人列席会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议听取和审议了县项目办《关于全县重点项目和十件实事建设的报告》；听取和审议了县人大财工委《关于对全县重点项目建设及十件实事办理情况的调查报告》；听取和审议了县规划执法局关于落实<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>两禁<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>决定、查处<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>两违<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>情况的报告；听取和审议了县发改局《关于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年上半年国民经济和社会发展计划执行情况及项目申报情况的报告》；听取和审议了县财政局《关于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年上半年财政预算执行情况的报告》；听取和审议了县人大财工委《关于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年上半年国民经济和社会发展计划执行及项目申报情况以及<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年上半年财政预算执行情况的调查报告》。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">李鹏谋要求，各级各部门要进一步增进共识，要坚定不移地推进<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">56</span>个重点项目建设；要进一步简化审批手续、抢抓时机招商引资、全力加快项目建设；要加大筹资力度，把加快项目建设、壮大规模企业作为培育税源的重要抓手，树立大抓项目、抓大项目的工作理念，培育一批新的经济增长点，做到人人身上有任务，人人肩上有责任，加快推进我县跨越式发展。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\">会前，与会人员</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">一行实地察看了三环线项目建设工地、南门大道项目建设工地、盛宇三期项目工程、永幸管业、武汉新联大、华亿通橡胶产业园、畈湖工业园、四邑新农村示范点</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据了解，南门大道已于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">27</span>日全面开工，目前已完成块石基础处理，排水主管及支管横穿已基本完成，清理主路基土层并碾压完工，计划<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>月底基本完成主干道商品工程；永幸管业项目于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2011</span>年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月动工，目前已建成宿舍楼一栋，办公楼一栋，职工食堂一栋，生产车间三栋和仓库三栋，预计在<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">6</span>月完成全部主体工程，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>月试投产；华亿通橡胶产业园正在进行车间和厂房的主体建设，整个基础设施建设正在有序推进，预计主体工程在<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>月底完工，首期工程在<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9</span>月底可以正式投入生产。<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-26/e77bd0fb3f64429ee2fb365125c89c5b.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n在武汉新联大生物科技有限公司检查</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1718','6','张姝、舒建华','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-26/ff30fe7fcbf13929c41e6551e35896a6.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议现场<br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">举报&ldquo;两非&rdquo;（非医学需要的胎儿性别鉴定、非医学需要的人工终止妊娠），一经查实即获</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元奖励。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">25</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，县卫生局在人民医院召开综合治理出生人口性别比暨打击&ldquo;两非&rdquo;公开处理大会，再加力度治理出生人口性别比，对&ldquo;两非&rdquo;行为亮剑。县委常委、宣传部长刘合权，副县长饶自斌，县政协副主席谢先火出席会议。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议学习传达了省卫生厅关于进一步加强出生人口性别比综合治理工作的通知，并通报了全县查处&ldquo;两非&rdquo;典型案件的相关情况，宣读了给予程珍红行政开除处分的决定和给予罗勇撤职处分的决定。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">记者从会上获悉，县卫生局从即日起停止五家医疗单位的</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">B</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">超业务（将</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">B</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">超集中封存）；同时加强与人口计生部门的信息沟通，配合做好&ldquo;两非&rdquo;案件的调查和处理，对举报人一经查实，除县里奖励外，卫生局还将给予</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万元的嘉奖。严厉禁止所有诊所、卫生室、医务室、卫生服务站、延伸门诊开展</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">B</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">超和终止妊娠业务。孕</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">14</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">周以上终止妊娠业务只能在指定的县人民医院、妇幼保健院和县计生服务站三家机构内实施，严厉禁止其它医疗机构开展孕</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">14</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">周以上终止妊娠业务。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">刘合权要求，对治理出生人口性别比和打击&ldquo;两非&rdquo;工作，认识上要再深化，做到零懈怠。全县所有从事妇产、药剂、</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">B</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">超业务的医务人员都是直接责任人，要有危机意识、责任意识和道德意识，都要吃透相关制度精神，知道哪些该做哪些不该做。他强调，卫生系统在管理上要再强化，做到零空档，各医疗机构要加强超声仪器的管理，对出现问题的有关医院停止一切</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">B</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">超业务，同时定期不定期开展检查督导和宣传教育，做到警钟长鸣，进一步规范医务人员从业行为。对&ldquo;两非&rdquo;案件的处理上要再钢化，做到零容忍，始终保持从严打击&ldquo;两非&rdquo;的高压态势。对违法违规行为予以坚决查处，对非医学需要鉴定胎儿性别和非医学需要的人工终止妊娠的医务人员一律实行&ldquo;双开一吊&rdquo;（即开除党籍、开除公职、吊销证照）。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">饶自斌指出，目前我县出生人口性别比形势严峻，卫生系统全体人员要高度重视，进一步落实疏导和预防责任，卫生、计生、药监等职能部门要加强对从业人员的教育和管理，落实责任追究机制；要进一步完善&ldquo;两非&rdquo;举报奖励制度，重奖重罚，不断提高&ldquo;两非&rdquo;案件查处力度和效果。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">卫生系统各单位一把手、计生专干，全县各级各类医疗机构妇产科、药剂科、</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">B</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">超室全体人员参加会议，并在会后进行了专业培训，集中学习《孕妇</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">B</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">超管理制度》、《终止妊娠药品管理制度》、《接生、不全流产、过期流产报告及死婴核查制度》等相关制度。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1719','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-29/c24c4ac3c328b311bcef916e59705507.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">在华亿通橡胶产业园参观<br />\r\n<img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-29/d473217dca09146895f81ed88129f617.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n参观在中能锂电项目</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"26\\\\\" month=\\\\\"7\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">26</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日上午</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，省经信委党组成员、总工程师陶红兵一行来到嘉鱼，考察我县承接武汉金口通用汽车产业基地配套项目进展情况。县长余珂，县委副书记李国光，副县长许隆高陪同考察。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">陶红兵一行先后参观考察了华亿通橡胶产业园、中能锂电项目、潘家湾多功能码头和沿江汽车产业园配套区，对我县得天独厚的区位交通、港口物流、产业载体、生产要素、基础配套等多方面的优势表示充分肯定。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据悉，嘉鱼与江夏区金口镇紧邻的沿江产业园配套区规划选址于沿江经济带咸嘉新城项目区，规划开发面积</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">20</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">平方公里，其中化工园区占地</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">平方公里，规划汽车工业园用地</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">平方公里。县委、县政府对该项目高度重视，迅速成立承接汽车产业配套项目领导小组，组建工作专班，多次召开专题工作会议，积极推进项目承接工作。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">我县已聘请上海同济规划设计院对嘉鱼进行&ldquo;一城、三镇、一区、三园&rdquo;的城市总体规划，已将承接汽车产业配套纳入了产业规划，并以京珠连接线、武深高速连接线为主轴，以&ldquo;五纵五横&rdquo;道路网络建设为中心，着力建设&ldquo;布局集中、用地集约、产业集聚、结构升级&rdquo;的汽车产业关联项目企业发展平台。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">目前，沿江汽车产业园中畈湖工业园正加快园区基础设施配套的建设进度，加快推进园区土地平整及道路建设、管网铺设；汽车产业配套区</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">平方公里已完成用地规划调整、拆迁、土方平整、排水、电、路等相关配套设施；已完成沿江汽车产业园配套区产业带畈湖工业园及嘉鱼经济开发区的整体环评、安评工作。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县发改局、经信局、招商局等部门主要负责人参加考察。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\" face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1720','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-29/552f0316ce9391cca1553d133f6ccbc8.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\">在归粮洲检查防汛</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">26</span>日下午，县长余珂，县委常委、县纪委书记魏朝东，县人大副主任贺隆君一行，在县水利部门负责人陪同下，深入新街镇归粮洲、四邑公堤防汛指挥部等地检查指导防汛工作，看望一线干部群众。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">余珂一行首先来到新街镇归粮洲，仔细察看水位情况以及是否存在散浸、管涌等险情，并向当班干部详细了解防汛责任落实、劳力安排、物资储备等情况。余珂强调，归粮洲防汛任务重，战线长，且区域内有万亩良田，关系到老百姓的切身利益，负责防汛人员切不可有麻痹思想，要密切关注水情、汛情与险情变化，并做好详细记录，对险情隐患早发现、早处置、早除险。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">随后，余珂一行来到四邑公堤防汛指挥部，看望坚守在这里的干部群众。余珂对他们坚守一线、连续作战的精神表示肯定，他说，全体党员干部要以对广大人民群众生命财产高度负责的精神，继续发扬艰苦奋斗的作风，加强巡堤查险，切切实实落实各项防汛抢险工作责任制，确保万无一失。 <span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据了解，我县有复兴洲、护县洲、归粮洲等民堤民垸共<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>处，分布在潘湾、鱼岳、牌洲等镇，保护农田面积达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">22</span>万余亩。以&ldquo;民堤按干堤标准防守&rdquo;、&ldquo;确保不丢一个民垸&rdquo;的原则，全县进入防汛实战状态。县防汛指挥部下设<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>个分指挥部和<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>个镇指挥部，人员全部到岗到位，实行<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>小时值班和严格交接班制度。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1721','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-29/c82e3a4c874b81109e88a0944dc6ec95.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\">在污水处理厂检查</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">26</span>日，由市政府副秘书长吴炳贵带队的市政府督查组来我县检查安居工程和总量减排工作，副县长许隆高陪同检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">督查组一行实地查看了嘉能热电有限公司，嘉鱼污水处理厂，栗山路公租、廉租房项目，沿湖大道棚户区改造项目。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">会上，许隆高向督查组汇报了我县保障性安居工程和总量减排工作进展情况。今年，我县开工建设廉租住房<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">160</span>套，公共租赁住房<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">400</span>套正在进行基础施工；城市棚户区改造即将开工建设<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">150</span>户。目前协议拆迁户<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">173</span>套，其中已拆除东岳路<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>户、大众<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">46</span>户，正在洽谈征收协议的鱼岳高中<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">103</span>户。垦区危房改造<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">450</span>户，目前已改造完工<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">259</span>户，计划年底全面完成。新增租赁补贴<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">400</span>户，至第二季度已完成<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">221</span>户。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">今年我县减排任务主要落实在联乐集团嘉鱼县富民酿造有限公司<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1200t/d</span>污水处理站建设项目、嘉鱼县嘉能热电有限公司双碱法脱硫项目、葛洲坝水泥有限公司新上低氮燃烧器项目以及嘉鱼县风华化工有限公司关停项目等四个项目上。预计可削减化学需氧量<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1990</span>吨，削减氨氮<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">925</span>吨，削减二氧化硫<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1250</span>吨，削减氮氧化物<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">300</span>吨。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">督查组一行对嘉鱼保障性安居工程和总量减排工作进展表示满意，认为嘉鱼县领导重视，部门联动，保障性安居工程和总量减排工作进展顺利。吴炳贵希望我县对存在的问题进行统筹谋划，加快棚户区改造项目的进度，使之和其它的安居工程齐头并进，尽量满足城镇低收入家庭住房要求；重点抓好联乐集团嘉鱼县富民酿造有限公司等四个项目，使之能够有效减排，确保年底全面完成保障性安居工程和总量减排任务。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1722','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-29/a5ac2ffd8495b7ef4a61984e53b7260f.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\">熊征宇一行查看珍湖围堤浑水漏洞险情</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"26\\\\\" month=\\\\\"7\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">26</span>日</st1:chsdate>，县委书记熊征宇来到陆溪镇珍湖围堤检查防汛工作，县领导李鹏谋、朱丛钦、魏萍陪同检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">下午三点，珍湖围堤<st1:chmetcnv w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"2800\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2800</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>处两辆卡车正在向围堤外侧倒土。原来，昨天巡堤人员在此处围堤内侧发现了一处浑水漏洞，该镇立即组织劳力搬运沙袋进行围堵，并开挖人字水沟，将渗透出来的水进行及时疏流。与此同时，该镇还组织车辆拖运石头、泥土等在围堤外侧进行了加固。据了解，这是该围堤目前出现的最大的险情，其他散浸、清水漏洞等<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">17</span>处轻微险情均已进行了有效控制。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">熊征宇指出，今年我县防汛重点是民堤民垸，珍湖民垸面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">9000</span>多亩，其中鱼池有<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2000</span>亩，如果弃守损失将非常惨重，因此负责该围堤的县领导、县民政局干部、陆溪镇村干部都要认识到防守此围堤的重要性，进一步增强责任感。他要求，防汛期间围堤不仅要上足劳力，而且技术人员要到位，尤其是重点险段要多安排经验足的防汛人员；要做好各项预案，做好打持久战的准备，将劳力、物资准备充足，遇到困难要及时向县防指报告。熊征宇还亲切地与坚守围堤的防汛人员一一握手，嘱咐他们注意自身安全以及施工安全。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">目前，陆溪镇已安排一支由<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">55</span>名干群组成的应急抢险队伍，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>小时不间断在珍湖围堤防守，确保安全。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1723','6','周艳','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-29/c0153f94039a2ca5717689706b126cca.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">座谈会现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><st1:chsdate w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\" isrocdate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" islunardate=\\\\\"False\\\\\" day=\\\\\"27\\\\\" month=\\\\\"7\\\\\" year=\\\\\"2012\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">27</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日</span></st1:chsdate><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，县委常委、宣传部长刘合权</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">带领县计生局相关工作人员，围绕年度目标管理责任指标和<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年人口计生工作要点，对鱼岳镇上半年人口和计划生育工作进行督办检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">刘合权认真听取了该镇计生工作情况汇报，并同计生专干进行了座谈，就一些重点难点问题进行了探讨和分析。刘合权说，人口和计划生育工作一直以来都是各级各部门常抓不懈的大事。根据调查摸底的情况看，鱼岳镇上半年的计生工作形势不容乐观，与年度目标管理责任指标的总体要求有一定差距。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">他要求，在下一阶段人口和计生工作中，鱼岳镇要进一步加强组织领导，充实计生队伍，全力打好人口计生攻坚战；要进一步加强宣传教育，营造浓厚的舆论氛围；要进一步强化孕情监测，形成严密的监控网络；要进一步加强对出生人口的清理清查，确保数据真实可靠；要进一步加大&ldquo;两非&rdquo;案件打击力度，继续保持高压态势，严格控制出生人口性别比，全力促进全县人口和计划生育工作健康稳步发展。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">座谈会上，县计生部门有关负责人就该镇人口和计划生育工作检查中，孕期随访、村居在线平台建设、长效节育措施落实等方面完成情况进行了通报反馈。</font></span>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-font-kerning: 0pt; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">当晚，刘合权一行还对官桥镇上半年人口和计划生育工作进行了督办检查。<br />\r\n</font></span><br />\r\n&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1724','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"http://www.cnjiayu.com.cn/uploadfile/2012/0727/20120727065818627.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\">考核组一行在实验中学检查</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">27</span>日，由省爱卫办副主任李建带队的考核组来我县检查验收灭蚊、灭蟑工作。县领导朱从钦、刘合权、饶自斌、雷家兴参加了上午召开的汇报会。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">当日下午，考核组分成<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>个小组按照<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>条路线，将利用<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>天时间深入到整个城区范围各支街小巷、饭馆、市场等地进行仔细检查，检查单位在<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>家以上，房间达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2000</span>个。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据了解，灭蚊、灭蟑工作是除&ldquo;四害&rdquo;工作中的一项，此次&ldquo;灭蚊、灭蟑先进城区&rdquo;创建工作达标是我县创建&ldquo;国家卫生县城&rdquo;的先决条件之一。县委、县政府高度重视此项工作，建立健全了除&ldquo;四害&rdquo;工作机制，开展多种形式的宣传教育，提高全民除&ldquo;四害&rdquo;意识。同时强化技术培训，定期组织县疾控中心专业技术员对有关职能部门及社区的骨干人员进行专业培训，详细讲解防治&ldquo;四害&rdquo;的科学知识与技能技巧。据统计，我县共发动群众<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">54000</span>多人次，动员单位、学校、社区开展清理居民小区、单位内外环境、集贸市场等虫害易滋生场所的垃圾、渣土等，不断通过实施环境整治，夯实除&ldquo;四害&rdquo;基础条件。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">近年来，我县累计投入除&ldquo;四害&rdquo;工作经费近<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">200</span>万元 ，每年开展春秋两季集中消杀活动，累计投放灭鼠毒饵<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24.5</span>吨、粘鼠板<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">378</span>块，灭蚊药剂<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3000</span>瓶，灭蟑胶饵<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">38000</span>支，各种喷雾器<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.8</span>万把。通过严格自查自纠，目前灭蚊、灭蟑各项监测指标全部达到了国家除&ldquo;四害&rdquo;合格标准。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1725','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-29/2a3109f8c3248bce6b4112d4b8e9f180.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\">图为会议现场</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">27</span>日，全县防汛工作会议召开。县领导熊征宇、余珂、李国光、李鹏谋、魏朝东、李新华、刘合权、李电波、贺隆君、戴书萍、魏萍、雷家兴、赵季明，县委办主任章斌出席会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">县委书记熊征宇指出，各镇各部门要从群众利益出发，从市委、市政府的要求出发，从历年和现在的防汛形势出发，树立不丢民堤民垸的思想准备；要根据后期的雨情、水情、汛情，做好打持久战的准备；要充分做好人员、物料等的准备，进一步加大查险、抢险、除险的准备，做到有险必查、有险必报；要做到统筹安排、科学调度、做好防汛抗旱工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">熊征宇要求，各镇各部门要统筹安排好民堤民垸的防守，物料的准备、人员的安排，统筹安排好防汛和抗旱工作，做到两手都要抓；防汛相关人员要严格遵守防汛抗旱的纪律，做到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>小时手机开机，外出（包括到武汉）要报告，对于擅离职守、贻误战机等违反纪律的行为要严肃处理。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">熊征宇强调，各镇各部门要充分认识到防汛工作的重要性，保持高度警惕，克服麻痹大意思想；要明确指导思想，把民堤民垸当作长江干堤来防，要严防死守，不能丢掉一个民堤民垸；要进一步明确防汛抗灾责任，将责任落实到人；要继续发扬不怕苦、不怕累、不怕疲劳的精神，继续奋战，夺取抗洪抢险的最后胜利。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">县长余珂要求各部门认真分析雨情和水情，强化打持久战的准备，加强值守和巡查，注重薄弱环节和薄弱时间的巡查；强化防汛物资的储备和管理，确保抢险物资及时到位；强化应急措施、应急队伍、应急机制的建立，确保一旦发生险情，没有人员伤亡；强化科学调度，对人员、物料、资金进行科学调度，合理安排。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">县委副书记李国光，县委常委、县纪委书记魏朝东，副县长魏萍分别就当前防汛工作进行了发言。各镇负责人分别汇报了前期防汛工作情况。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据了解，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">27</span>日下午<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>时，三峡水库下泄流量将增加到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">45000</span>立方米每秒。另根据气象部门分析预测，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">28</span>日至<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">29</span>日，长江上游一般为小雨，局地中雨；中游地区有阵雨，局地中雨。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>日&mdash;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>日，金沙江、嘉陵江、汉江上游有中雨，局地大到暴雨，我县永逸闸水位明日仍呈上涨趋势，涨幅在<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0.05</span>米以内，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">29</span>日水位将持平，此次洪峰嘉鱼站将接近警戒水位。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1726','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-29/67054ac22fab7da8c167791c164b1d06.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n会议现场<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">28</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，县委常委、宣传部长刘合权，副县长魏萍带领县委办、政府办、县计生局相关工作人员，对陆溪镇现阶段人口和计划生育工作进行检查督办。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">刘合权、魏萍认真听取了该镇计生工作情况汇报和县计生部门入户调查摸底情况汇报。刘合权说，自</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">23</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日县综合治理&ldquo;两非&rdquo;工作会后，陆溪镇迅速传达落实了会议精神，想了很多办法，采取了很多措施。但根据这次调查摸底的情况来看，计生工作虽有亮点和特色，但是效果不明显，形势不容乐观，与年度目标管理责任指标的总体要求仍有一定差距。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">刘合权要求，陆溪镇要进一步加强组织领导，强化各级党政领导责任，科学统筹人口计生工作，实行主要领导负总责、亲自抓，分管领导具体抓、班子成员合力抓，形成齐抓共管的局面；要全面彻底的对出生人口开展清理清查，掌握孕情，实行名单化管理；要进一步加强宣传教育，营造浓厚的舆论氛围；要进一步加大&ldquo;两非&rdquo;案件打击力度，继续保持高压态势，严格控制出生人口性别比，全力促进全县人口和计划生育工作健康稳步发展。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">魏萍要求，陆溪镇要正视问题，采取强有力措施，推进计划生育工作；要进一步强化孕情监测，形成严密的监控网络；要充分发挥利益导向作用，提高优质服务水平，落实优惠倾斜政策；要加大综合治理力度，对违反计划生育政策的，该上硬措施的要上硬措施，重点纠治出生人口性别比失衡问题，全力打好人口计生攻坚战。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">座谈会上，县计生部门有关负责人就该镇人口和计划生育工作检查中，孕期随访、村居在线平台建设、长效节育措施落实等方面完成情况进行了通报反馈。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><o:p><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">&nbsp;</font></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1727','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-29/8e9ffadd4d1c77950768617abe548dfa.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-29/4e7bbeebbf7187da4005f47bee061cdd.jpg\\\\\" /></o:p></span></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">28</span>日，嘉鱼县创&ldquo;灭蚊、灭蟑先进城区&rdquo;达标考核情况通报会召开。省爱卫办考核组通报了考核结果，宣布我县创&ldquo;灭蚊、灭蟑先进城区&rdquo;达标考核通过。县领导余珂、朱丛钦、刘合权、雷家兴出席会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">省爱卫办考核组通过听汇报、查阅资料以及分组进行现场检查后，一致认为我县高度重视除<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&ldquo;</span>四害<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">&rdquo;</span>工作，宣传发动深入，措施得力，灭蚊、灭蟑成效显著，达到了有关规定的标准，同意通过考核。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">县长余珂出席会议并讲话，他对省爱卫办考核专家组多次深入嘉鱼，对我县除&ldquo;四害&rdquo;工作进行悉心指导表示感谢。他说，考核组此次对我县&ldquo;灭蚊、灭蟑&rdquo;工作的肯定既是鼓舞也是鞭策，下一阶段我县将对照考核组提出的建议，重点做好&ldquo;建&rdquo;的工作，完善城市基础设施，改善城区面貌；进一步做好&ldquo;管&rdquo;的工作，落实长效管理机制，巩固好前一阶段的创建成果；加大&ldquo;创&rdquo;的力度，进一步营造浓厚的创建氛围，提高市民创卫意识。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">据了解， &ldquo;灭蚊、灭蟑先进城区&rdquo;达标考核是创建全国卫生县城的一项重要指标，此次考核通过将为我县创建全国卫生县城打下良好的基础。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1728','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-30/520e7fa3eeccf1f56725280a52b043ec.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">在谷洲围堤查看险情<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-30/d99ca15abd94f68b4938d5266aa66105.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">在归粮洲围堤了解汛情<br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">29</span>日上午，县委书记熊征宇，县委常委、县纪委书记魏朝东来到谷洲围堤、归粮洲围堤，查看汛情并慰问坚守一线的防汛人员。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">谷洲围堤<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4100</span>米处曾经是该围堤弃守的倒口位置，倒口处的复堤比较薄弱，近日该处出现了多处散浸险情。现场，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>多名防汛人员正在顶着烈日开挖人字型水沟，进行及时导滤，控制险情。熊征宇要求该围堤防汛指挥部尽快组织人员将地面杂草清除干净，方便及时发现险情。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">归粮洲围堤目前水位<st1:chmetcnv tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"29.8\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">29.8</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>，已超保证水位近<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1.3</span>米。站在堤上，记者看到，外江水位已经超过了堤面，水浪轻轻拍打着堤面上抢筑的<st1:chmetcnv tcsc=\\\\\"0\\\\\" numbertype=\\\\\"1\\\\\" negative=\\\\\"False\\\\\" hasspace=\\\\\"False\\\\\" sourcevalue=\\\\\"1500\\\\\" unitname=\\\\\"米\\\\\" w:st=\\\\\"on\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1500</span>米</st1:chmetcnv>子堤。新街镇党委书记杨新武带病坚守在堤上已经<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>多天了，他介绍说该围堤每天保证<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100</span>名劳力<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>小时坚守，吃住在堤上，严防死守。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">熊征宇表示，目前长江水位不见下降，各民堤高水位浸泡的时间将会延长，各民堤防汛指挥部要克服麻痹思想，做好打持久战的准备。他对坚守一线的防汛人员说，越是关键时刻，越不能放松，时刻把查险、除险作为工作重点，同时做好各项应急预案，确保安全。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-30/2ede6bb92b1d46afdd50806679960701.jpg\\\\\" /></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 16px\\\\\">防汛人员开挖导滤沟</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt\\\\\"><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1729','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-30/97f496f632c0d578a657294338eff298.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">考核组参观二乔公园<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-30/df7c65d04111dbf025c6bb98b57bf553.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">汇报会现场<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">28</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，省园林城市考核组一行赴嘉鱼县，对我县获得&ldquo;省级园林城市&rdquo;光荣称号以来的创建工作进行复查。副县长李德炳陪同检查。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">考核组一行实地参观了城南生态公园、人民公园、二乔公园、沙滩浴场、环湖公园等地，对我县近年来在园林创建方面所取得的成果给予充分肯定。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据悉，我县自</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2009</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年成功创建&ldquo;湖北园林县城&rdquo;以来，为深入巩固创建成果，加快县中心城区园林绿化建设，促进城市生态可持续发展，创造更加优美的人居环境，进行了多举措、全方位的深入推进。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">三年来，在巩固省级园林县城创建工作中，我县形成了点、线、面结合的城市园林绿化体系。截至目前，建成区绿地率、绿化覆盖率和人均公园绿地面积分别达到</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">39%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">、</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">45%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">和</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">10.8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">平方米，城市道路绿化普及率和达标率分别达到</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">95.49%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">和</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">81%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">。同时，我县还加大了大环境绿化建设、生态环境治理、市政基础设施建设力度，并取得了明显成效。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">考核组通过实地察看和听取汇报、翻阅资料，对我县近年来城市建设和园林绿化取得的成绩一致表示肯定，尤其是二乔公园、环湖公园等景观的建成，增加了城市绿量和道路绿量，提高了人居环境质量和城市文化品味，提升了城市形象。考核组要求我县在下一步工作中，进一步提高对创建园林城市的认识，形成人人参与创建的浓厚氛围；进一步完善城市管理措施，制定各项规章制度，确保来之不易的创建成果得到巩固。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县政府办副主任李黄金，县规划局局长何晓山陪同检查。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1730','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">29</span>日下午，县领导李鹏谋、魏朝东、朱从钦赴陆溪镇珍湖围堤、虎山围堤检查重点险情堤段，指导防汛人员及时除险。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">在珍湖围堤<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2800</span>米处出现的浑水漏洞险情处，记者看到，经过内筑围堰蓄水反压、外帮粘土堵截漏洞的方式及时处理后，直径<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>米宽的围堰中漏洞还在缓缓向外冒水，不过水质由浑变清，险情得到明显控制。了解情况后，县领导要求此处防守人员要继续密切关注险情，<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">24</span>小时监控，出现异常情况及时向指挥部汇报。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">随后县领导一行又来到虎山围堤，该堤<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">28</span>日出现一处浑水漏洞，指挥部已组织劳力筑起了小围堰。目前围堰已经被漏洞冒出的泥沙堵得严严实实，几乎看不到水往外冒。根据防汛经验，县领导认为：&ldquo;没有水往外冒，情况不对劲！&rdquo;于是立即指挥在场劳力对围堰进行清理疏通，经过仔细观察，该处浑水漏洞由于导滤及时，已经转化为散浸。县领导强调，虽然险情得到控制，但是此处系白蚁筑巢，不可麻痹大意，要对周围堤面加强巡查力度，确保及时发现险情及时除险。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1731','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-07-31/76263645202bbedf2db711c0d7887e45.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n听取情况介绍<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">30</span>日，县长余珂来到洲湾镇长江干堤检查防汛工作。县领导许标、李新华、房健、曾祥坤、魏萍陪同检查。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">余珂一行实地查看了州湾镇双益进洪闸、月亮湾险段、河埠进洪闸、幸福垸等地。每到一处，余珂都与值守人员交谈，详细了解当前防汛情况和存在的突出问题及采取的主要措施。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">余珂指出，据气象和水利部门通报，由于三峡泄洪和上游来水，当前高水位将持续到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">5</span>日，甚至更长时间，许多地方都已达到或接近警戒水位。各部门一定要认清当前严峻的防汛抗洪形势，坚决克服麻痹侥幸思想，时刻保持高度警惕，认真做好各项准备工作。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">余珂强调，各镇各部门要进一步落实好防汛责任制、汛期值班制，严肃防汛纪律，加大对当前防汛工作的监督检查力度，确保领导到位、责任到位、措施到位；要加强隐患排查，对病险地段做到心中有数；要完善防汛抢险各项预案，坚决打好防汛抗洪攻坚战；要备足备齐抢险物料，保障堤坝道路畅通，确保各类工程机械、物资和人员能够及时投入防汛抢险。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">据了解，今日洲湾永逸闸水位为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">28.67</span>米，超警戒水位<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0.17</span>米。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1732','6','熊铁山','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-08-01/104d6dbbce3d6ac9cfe39dfe83e69346.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n与消防官兵亲切握手<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">31</span>日上午，县委书记熊征宇，县委副书记、县长余珂等县四大家领导，先后来到县人武部、光荣院、武警中队、军休所和消防大队等地慰问部队官兵和离退休军转干部，向他们致以节日的问候，并送上慰问金。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;八一建军节就要到了，我代表县委、县政府来看望你们，祝大家节日快乐！&rdquo;每到一处，熊征宇一行都与官兵们亲切握手，详细了解他们的工作、生活情况，向他们送上节日的祝福。官兵们则用热烈的掌声、整齐的队列欢迎县领导的到来。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 12pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">&ldquo;感谢大家历年来积极参与我县防汛抗旱、抢险救灾等各种任务，为保障嘉鱼人民的生命财产安全、维护社会稳定作出的巨大贡献！&rdquo;在武警中队，熊征宇代表全县人民为武警战士们送去最诚挚的祝福，并希望广大官兵继续发扬光荣传统和优良作风，不断提高军事素质，为建设和谐嘉鱼再立新功。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-inden