E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1734','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">为庆祝中国人民解放军建军</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">85</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">周年，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">31</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，嘉鱼县召开军民联谊座谈会。在喜庆、融洽的气氛中，县领导与军民代表欢聚一堂，畅谈嘉鱼发展好形势，共叙军民鱼水深情。县委常委、常务副县长熊武华，县委常委、县人武部部长王俊，县人大副主任曾祥坤，县政协副主席谢先火，县人武部政委高超出席座谈会。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">熊武华代表县四大家及</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">37</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万嘉鱼人民向驻嘉部队全体官兵致以节日的问候和祝愿。他说，多年来，驻嘉部队官兵始终保持和发扬了人民军队的优良传统和作风，在完成战备训练任务、加强自身全面建设的同时，认真践行我军宗旨、积极发挥参建作用，真正把我县当故乡，积极投身我县经济建设，广泛开展军地共建、扶贫帮困等活动。在推进我县发展上勇挑重担，在扶贫帮困中争做表率，在抢险救灾中勇当先锋，为改变县城面貌做出了积极贡献，有力地推动了我县经济社会又好又快发展，赢得了人民群众的广泛赞誉。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">高超说，人武部是军地双方沟通的桥梁和纽带，除努力加强自身建设外，还要充分发挥部队优势，积极参与地方经济社会发展，协助地方党委政府维护社会稳定，与嘉鱼人民同呼吸、共命运、心连心，为&ldquo;打造湖北经济强县，建设长江临港新城&rdquo;作出自己的贡献。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">据悉，嘉鱼县素有拥军优属、拥政爱民的光荣传统。县委、县政府一直关心支持人武部的建设成长，认真落实各项党管武装制度，不断规范党管武装内容。坚持做到了&ldquo;十个纳入&rdquo;：把人武部建设纳入了嘉鱼经济社会发展统一规划，把人武工作纳入县委、县政府议事日程统一部署，把人武工作职责落实情况纳入党政部门和主要领导实绩考核内容统一考评，把人武经费纳入财政统一保障，把人武干部队伍纳入党政干部体系统一建设，把人武政策法规纳入地方立法、普法计划统一落实，把国防教育纳入党政机关理论学习和国民教育内容统一实施，把人武力量建设参建参治纳入我县经济社会建设统一组织，把军事设施安全纳入社会综合治理统一部署，把军转干部安置、随军家属就业、子女入学入托和涉军维权纳入双拥工作统一安排。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1735','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-08-01/7cece068a8bd4d1f72eff81cce68a9c8.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-size: medium\\\\\">余珂向防汛人员了解情况</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">7</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">31</span>日，县长余珂赴复兴洲围堤检查防汛工作，看望慰问坚守在一线的防汛人员。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">复兴洲面积<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2.4</span>万多亩，种植有棉花、稻谷、湘莲等农作物，是一片土壤肥沃的良田。为了保住复兴洲，潘家湾镇和当地村组干部、群众纷纷主动上堤进行防守，防汛积极性很高。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">复兴洲围堤长<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">18.6</span>公里，目前该围堤外江水位达到<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">29.4</span>米，超过了保证水位。由于长时间高水位的浸泡，近日在该围垸北面围堤出现了长达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">400</span>米的散浸群，防汛人员正在进行开挖人形沟，将积水及时导出，防止更大险情出现。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">县长余珂来到散浸险情处进行了仔细查看，向技术人员询问险情处理情况，了解该围堤其它地方是否出现险情等。他强调，复兴洲面积较大，一旦弃守损失严重；同时，该围堤防守战线较长，因此要加大防守力度，克服厌战和麻痹思想，确保该围垸万无一失。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1736','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-08-02/47e466a6a81a474deed84c6bd5e9b479.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会议现场<br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，市人大代表建议（咸潘一级公路）督办会在我县召开。市人大副主任周亨华，县长余珂、县人大副主任谢望松、副县长李德炳、县政协副主席刘平出席会议。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">周亨华说，咸潘一级公路的建设既是群众的呼声，也是经济社会发展的迫切需要，市人大常委会对该建议高度重视。他要求我县在前期所取得的工作成效基础上，进一步统一思想，明确目标，抓紧工作进度，迅速开展征地拆迁等相关工作；要抓紧招投标工作，早日确定施工单位和监理单位；要抓紧招商项目的洽谈，确保咸潘一级公路改建工程如期完工。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">余珂介绍了我县咸潘一级公路改建工程概况以及前期工作情况。咸潘一级公路改建工程起于温泉三班口，止于潘家湾镇码头，全长</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">47.519</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">公里，我县境内长</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">15.59</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">公里。目前项目初步设计已完成，并进行了外业验收，正转入内业设计。我县已成立了咸潘一级公路改建工程指挥部，目前已完成征地拆迁登记和田路分家工作。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1737','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-08-02/f6fa0df4e01d2752fac59d1ca8c2880a.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></font></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">31</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日下午，嘉鱼县&ldquo;八一&rdquo;座谈暨双拥&ldquo;三百&rdquo;活动动员会在县人武部召开。县委常委、县人武部部长王俊，副县长魏萍，县人武部政委高超出席会议。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议首先传达了省军区政治部、省双拥办联合下发的《关于在全省开展双拥&ldquo;三百&rdquo;活动的意见》。文件指出，要在全省广泛开展军民共建百个和谐社区、&ldquo;驻鄂部队联系帮扶百家光荣院（福利院）&rdquo;、&ldquo;军民共办百场文艺晚会&rdquo;活动（简称双拥&ldquo;三百&rdquo;活动）。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">魏萍就全县双拥&ldquo;三百&rdquo;活动的开展作了要求和部署。她说，全县各部门各单位要服从和服务于双拥创建工作的整体目标，密切配合，协同作战，切实加强活动的组织和协调；要加强宣传发动，使双拥创建和&ldquo;三百&rdquo;活动深入人心，家喻户晓，进一步形成军爱民、民拥军的良好社会风尚；双拥工作要注重实效，积极开展科技拥军、文化拥军和智力拥军活动，帮助部队培养技术人才，扶持部队开展科技练兵活动，为实现科技强军多做贡献。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">与会的县人武部、武警中队、消防大队、光荣院等单位就双拥&ldquo;三百&rdquo;活动的开展，分别作了表态发言。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1738','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-08-02/432f1fc9e13aec876ddd9353bd1adcb7.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会议现场<br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">日，由市委副秘书长、市创建办主任郑俊华带队的市目标责任制年中检查组一行，赴嘉鱼县就上半年目标责任制落实情况进行检查。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">会上，县委副书记李国光汇报了我县</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2012</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">年上半年目标责任制落实情况。今年以来，我县克服宏观经济形势的不利影响，紧紧围绕市定目标，全面加快&ldquo;经济强县、临港新城、旅游胜地、鱼米之乡、幸福家园&rdquo;建设，实现了县域经济平稳较快增长。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">上半年，全县完成地区生产总值</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">61.31</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，占全年目标的</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">40.1%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">，同比增长</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">12.8%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">；完成固定资产投资</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">68.7</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，占年目标的</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">60.3%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">、增长</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">41.1%</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">；完成规模工业增加值</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">39.02</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，完成地方一般预算收入</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3.34</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元，完成社会消费品零售总额</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">15.16</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">亿元、外贸出口</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1856.4</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">万美元。上半年，我县规模工业增加值增幅位居全市第二，固定资产投资、社会消费品零售总额、外贸出口等指标增幅位居全市第一。</span></font></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">通过听取情况汇报，市考核组认为，我县提前部署、提前谋划，半年经济运行质量高、经济发展指标完成情况良好；社会发展的各项工作做得十分扎实，取得了一定成效；坚持了稳定第一责任，社会治安环境良好，为经济发展提供了坚实保障。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">为更好的抓好下半年目标责任制的落实，市考核组要求我县进一步抢抓区位、交通等机遇，加大招商引资力度，紧盯大项目，以项目促进城市基础设施建设和旅游业的发展；要进一步加大城市建设管理力度，在创建全国文明县城的基础上，继续创建全国卫生县城；加大对社会重大矛盾、纠纷案件的排查力度，确保圆满完成全年的各项目标任务。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1739','6','张姝','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-08-03/9ad2b8615603d9a0360727cc35846572.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">在鱼岳镇护城堤指挥部了解情况<br />\r\n</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">月</font><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font><font face=\\\\\"宋体\\\\\">日，市水务局局长宋旭余赴嘉鱼县检查长江干堤防汛度汛工作。县领导李鹏谋、魏朝东、朱从钦、李电波陪同检查。</font></span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">宋旭余一行先后来到鱼岳镇护城堤防汛指挥部、陆溪镇防汛指挥部及长江干堤沿线各哨所，向当班值守人员详细了解当前防汛情况和存在的突出问题及采取的主要措施。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">宋旭余指出，当前防汛工作已进入关键时期，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">防汛人员</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">要发扬艰苦奋斗、连续作战的精神，克服因</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">天气炎热、工作疲劳</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">而产生的</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">厌战情绪</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">，</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">要做好打持久战的充分准备</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">；各级各部门要</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">在思想上、组织上、措施上做好充分准备，严格检查落实防汛责任制，完善防汛各项预案，加强汛情监测预报工作，优化调度科学防控，坚持防汛值班制度，确保安全度汛。</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">据悉，我县防汛指挥部下设</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">7</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">个分指挥部和</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">8</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">个镇指挥部，人员全部到岗到位，实行</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">24</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;; font-size: 12pt; mso-spacerun: \\\\''yes\\\\''\\\\\">小时值班和严格交接班制度。在长江干堤的防守上，严格落实&ldquo;责任领导到位、技术力量到位、防守劳力到位&rdquo;。县防指每天针对长江水情和汛情，及时会商，科学调度，充分储备人力、物力、财力。<br />\r\n<span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\"><br />\r\n</span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"p0\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin-top: 15.6pt; text-indent: 21pt; margin-bottom: 15.6pt\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1740','6','熊铁山、李娜','中国嘉鱼网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">8</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">月</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">1</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">日下午，省农业厅副巡视员杨华林一行来嘉鱼县检查督导水稻主要病虫害防控工作情况。市农业局总农艺师陈绪构、副县长魏萍等陪同检查。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">杨华林一行深入到鱼岳镇陆码头村实地查看了水稻病虫害情况，他表示，嘉鱼农业病虫害得到很好的预防和控制，水稻生长情况良好，为确保我县粮食生产安全和质量安全打下了良好的基础。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">连日来的高温天气持续，为防范高温热害和病虫害的影响，确保今年中稻有个好收成，鱼岳镇积极应对，采取镇干部包村、村干部包组、农技人员包田块的包保责任制，根据田块特点和生育进程，指导农民采取相对应的技术措施。该镇成立了</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">2</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">个机防队，配置</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">60</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">余台喷雾机，每台机器每天可完成喷药</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">40</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">亩，</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">3</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">天即可完成一次大面积的病虫害普防。</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">由于及时采取了合理指导、适时监控、统防统治等一系列举措，鱼岳镇</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\"><font face=\\\\\"Times New Roman\\\\\">11000</font></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt; mso-ascii-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''; mso-bidi-font-size: 10.0pt\\\\\">亩的水稻主要病虫害得到有效地防控，确保了中稻的丰产丰收。</span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1741','6','刘蒙','中国嘉鱼网','<div style=\\\\\"text-align: center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><img alt=\\\\\"\\\\\" src=\\\\\"/d/file/jiayuzhengwu/zhengwudongtai/2012-08-03/62bb380636a7b3962fadd6aa602dbcbd.jpg\\\\\" /><br />\r\n</font></span></div>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">8</span>月<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>日，嘉鱼县城市总体规划方案征求部门意见座谈会召开。副县长李德炳出席会议，全县各乡镇及相关部门共<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">37</span>家单位代表参加会议。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">会上，县规划局负责人向与会人员介绍了我县新一轮城市总体规划修编工作的进展情况，上海同济城市规划设计院该项目负责人介绍了我县城市总体规划初稿方案。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">我县新一轮城市总体规划从今年<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>月份开始编制，上海同济城市规划设计院专家组在我县进行了现状调查，组织召开了一系列座谈会，实地走访和调研相关地区，收集和整理了大量基础资料，目前已完成规划方案初稿。总规规划期限为<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2011</span>&mdash;<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2030</span>年，对我县城市性质定位为武汉城市圈内以现代农业、新型工业、综合物流为主导的长江港口城市，具有水乡人文特色的宜居宜游生态城市。与会<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">37</span>个相关部门代表纷纷发言，对新出炉的规划方案表示大致赞同，并各抒己见，提出了许多建设性的建议和意见。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\">李德炳对编制单位前段艰苦细致、富有成效的工作予以充分肯定。他表示，新的规划方案应立足嘉鱼当前实际、着眼嘉鱼发展方向，在城市定位方面进一步提炼。总规方案还要与各相关部门正在实施或准备实施的规划相结合，充分凸显出嘉鱼的特色，要结合与会人员的意见并多渠道吸收各方意见作进一步的修改。</font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 宋体\\\\\"><font size=\\\\\"3\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></font></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 24pt; margin: 16.3pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\">&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1742','7','县政府办','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">嘉政办发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2012]82</span>号<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">各镇人民政府，县政府各部门，嘉鱼经济开发区管委会：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 32.25pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">经县人民政府同意，现将《嘉鱼县<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年食品安全工作方案》印发给你们，请认真遵照执行。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 259pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 18.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 二<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0</span>一二年七月六日<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-indent: 296pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 18.5\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 15.6pt; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt\\\\\">嘉鱼县<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年食品安全工作方案<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">为进一步做好我县<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年食品安全工作，规范食品生产经营行为，保障食品安全，根据《国务院办公厅关于印发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年食品安全重点工作安排的通知》（国办发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2012]16</span>号）和《市人民政府办公室关于印发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2012</span>年咸宁市食品安全工作方案的通知》（咸政办函<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2012]24</span>号）精神，结合我县实际，制定本方案。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">一、指导思想<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">以邓小平理论、&ldquo;三个代表&rdquo;重要思想和科学发展观为指导，认真贯彻落实党的十七届六中全会、全省经济工作会议、市第四次党代会及全省食品安全工作会议精神，按照&ldquo;标本兼治、着力治本、突出重点、全面治理&rdquo;的工作原则，全面落实&ldquo;地方政府负总责、监管部门各负其责、企业负主体责任&rdquo;的食品安全责任体系；进一步创新监管工作机制和方法，深入推进食品安全专项整治，规范食品市场秩序；加强基层监管队伍建设，不断完善监管责任制和监管网络；强化食品安全日常监管，提升监管效能，健全食品安全监管长效机制，促进食品安全水平不断提高。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">二、工作任务与目标<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）进一步完善分工负责与统一协调相结合的食品安全监管体制机制，食品安全综合协调机构健全、职责明确、制度完善。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）食品安全日常监督检查覆盖率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>，食品安全工作纳入目标管理的考核率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>，餐饮业食品安全量化分级管理率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">80%</span>以上。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）初级农产品种养殖、食品生产、食品流通、餐饮服务环节食品抽检合格率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">90%</span>以上，生猪定点屠宰率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（四）进一步规范食品生产加工小作坊和食品摊贩的生产经营活动，对幼儿园、中小学校周边食品小作坊和摊贩的无证生产经营取缔率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（五）食品生产、食品流通、餐饮服务企业的索票索证记录保存率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>，可追溯率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（六）食品安全举报投诉登记齐全，调查处理率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（七）食品生产经营企业负责人培训率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">90%</span>以上，公众食品安全满意度达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">95%</span>以上。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（八）不断提升食品安全事故的应急处置能力，食品安全事故妥善处置率达<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">100%</span>，不发生</span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"mso-no-proof: yes\\\\\">III</span></span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">级以上食品安全事故。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">三、 工作措施<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）健全食品安全监管体制机制。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">明确监管部门职责，健全食品安全综合协调机构，进一步完善食品安全监管体制机制。加强基层食品安全建设，全面建设食品药品安全监管站，落实镇政府及监管站的食品安全职责，推行监管中心下移，建立纵向到底、横向到边的全覆盖监管网络，筑牢食品安全防线，消除监管漏洞和盲区。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）深化食品安全治理整顿。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">继续开展严厉打击食品非法添加和滥用食品添加剂专项治理行动，加大对超范围、超限量使用食品添加剂问题的治理力度；深入开展乳制品、食用油、肉类、酒类、食品添加剂、保健食品综合治理，集中开展食品交易市场、农村食品市场、城乡结合部、&ldquo;城中村&rdquo;、工地、中小学校食堂和校园周边等重点场所整治；加大对食用农产品农药、兽药残留监测力度，组织开展畜禽屠宰、调味品、餐具及食品包装材料的专项整治，进一步整顿规范小作坊、小摊贩、小餐饮单位等薄弱环节的食品生产经营行为；严厉打击生产销售伪劣食品及假冒伪劣包装材料的&ldquo;黑窝点&rdquo;，全面排查并严厉惩处&ldquo;地沟油&rdquo;、&ldquo;瘦肉精&rdquo;、利用病死畜禽加工食品的违法犯罪行为。保持&ldquo;挖隐患、抓反复、防反弹&rdquo;的高压态势，坚决防止社会影响和危害较大的食品安全问题发生。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）加强食品安全日常监管检查。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">强化农业、卫生、质监、工商等部门食品安全日常监督检查的责任，扩大监督抽查的频次、范围，对存在严重食品安全问题的，要依法加大行政处罚力度，直至停产整改、吊销证照；对隐瞒食品安全隐患、故意逃避监管等行为，要依法从重处理。深入排查食用农产品生产、食品生产加工、流通、餐饮服务等环节的食品安全隐患，确保米、面、食用油、鲜肉和肉制品、乳制品、水产品、儿童食品、老年食品、学生供餐以及酒类等食品安全。健全完善食品抽检制度，加大食品安全监督抽检。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（四）落实食品生产经营者的主体责任。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">进一步规范许可程序，完善食品生产经营许可审查规范，严把准入关。加强对农村义务教育学生供餐等集中供餐单位的源头监管。强化食品生产经营企业内部管理，明确主管责任人和关键岗位的责任。严格执行食品从业人员每年不少于<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">40</span>小时的培训制度，提高食品从业人员的食品安全意识和能力。制定完善食品生产加工环节不合格食品召回、流通环节不合格食品退市和销毁管理制度，防止过期、腐败变质等不合格食品回流生产经营环节。推进食品企业信用体系建设，加大对失信企业惩戒力度，全面建立食品生产经营单位信用档案，实施分级分类监管。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（五）提高食品安全监管执法能力。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">加大财政投入力度，保障行政监管和刑事执法装备、检测设备和工作经费。加强基层监管执法队伍和技术装备建设，强化监管人员培训考核，规范执法程序，提高监管执法队伍依法行政的能力和侦查办案水平。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（六）提升食品安全事件的应急处置能力。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">组织修订食品安全事故应急预案，建立健全食品安全事故快速反应和查处机制，组建应急处置专家队伍，加强应急演练和培训，提升指挥协调和现场处置能力。健全食品安全信息报送体系，细化完善信息报送时限、程序、责任等方面的要求。建立重大食品安全信息发布的评估审核制度，确保信息发布及时、准确、客观。监督、指导食品生产经营企业制定食品安全事故处置方案，提高其应对突发事件能力。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（七）加强食品安全风险监测和评估工作。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">强化对食品安全风险预警、监测、评估和交流工作，加强综合协调，统筹农业、卫生、质监、工商、食品药品监管等部门的食品安全风险监测和食品抽检工作，组织实施国家食品和食用农产品安全风险监测年度计划，开展食品和食用农产品安全风险评估。统筹食品检验检测队伍建设，开展检验检测资源整合试点，避免重复建设。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（八）继续开展食品安全示范建设。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">在食品生产、经营、消费环节开展食品安全示范和诚信建设，组织开展餐饮服务食品安全&ldquo;三个一&rdquo;示范创建活动和食品流通环节&ldquo;食品安全示范店&rdquo;评定表彰活动，推进食品安全先进县创建活动。以创建食品安全示范县为契机，全面开展示范一条街、示范镇、示范单位创建活动，实行以点带面，示范带动，不断探索科学监管模式，进一步提升食品安全保障水平。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; vertical-align: baseline; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">（九）深入开展食品安全宣传教育。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">本着&ldquo;面向基层、面向群众、贴近生活、接近实际&rdquo;的宣传原则，充分利用电视台、电台、报纸、网络等多种新闻媒体，大力宣传食品安全法律法规和科普知识。</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">一是继续通过开展<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3.15</span>集中宣传、食品安全宣传周、食品安全&ldquo;</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">进学校、进社区、进农村、进企业、进机关、进家庭&rdquo;等宣传</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">活动，提高广大群众的食品安全意识和自我保护能力，积极引导社会参与食品安全工作。二是办好《聚焦食品药品安全》专栏节目，利用专家讲座普及食品安全知识，及时曝光食品安全典型案例，促进行业自律，引导公众安全消费。三是支持新闻媒体开展舆论监督，加强舆情监测，及时核查反映出的食品安全问题。加强社会舆论的正面引导，及时准确地通报食品安全形势和监管信息。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; vertical-align: baseline; mso-pagination: none; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">四、工作要求<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; vertical-align: baseline; mso-pagination: none; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">（一）加强组织领导， 增强责任意识。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">各镇政府要进一步落实食品安全属地管理责任，将食品安全工作列入重要议事日程，加强对本地区食品安全工作的统一领导，组织协调。要结合各镇实际制定食品安全工作实施方案，细化目标任务，逐级落实责任。各级食安办要加强综合协调和督促检查，确保各项工作落实到位。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; vertical-align: baseline; mso-pagination: none; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">（二）加强综合协调，提高监管合力。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">各食品安全监管部门要认真履行职责，相互衔接，分兵把守，形成完整的监管链，提高监管合力。建立违法案件查处&ldquo;首责制&rdquo;，消除监管盲区和死角，有效杜绝有案不查、推诿扯皮等问题。县食安办要认真做好综合协调工作，形成上下联动、部门联动、地区联动的执法格局和对食品安全违法行为的打击合力。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28.1pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; vertical-align: baseline; mso-pagination: none; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">（三）加强信息管理，做好应急处置。</span></b><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: \\\\''Times New Roman\\\\''\\\\\">各镇政府和各监管部门要畅通食品安全信息渠道，加强工作沟通，有效应对和及时处置突发食品安全事件。切实加强食品安全舆情监测工作，提高食品安全风险的识别能力，有效排除食品安全风险。按规定及时报送食品安全风险监测信息，实施发布食品安全风险预警。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 27pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-alt: 0pt\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>');");
E_D("replace into `phome_ecms_news_data_1` values('1743','7','县政府办','嘉鱼政务网','<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 31pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; line-height: 31pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 15pt\\\\\">嘉政办发<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">[2012]84</span>号<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 31pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><b style=\\\\\"mso-bidi-font-weight: normal\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-size: 18pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></b></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">各镇人民政府，县政府各部门，嘉鱼经济开发区管委会：<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 33pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">经县人民政府同意，现将《嘉鱼县地方税费征收保障工作目标管理考核办法》印发给你们，请认真遵照执行。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 31pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 31pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 31pt; text-indent: 238pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 17.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 二<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">0</span>一二年七月十六日<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 31pt; text-indent: 288pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 18.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 31pt; text-indent: 288pt; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-char-indent-count: 18.0; mso-line-height-rule: exactly\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" align=\\\\\"center\\\\\" style=\\\\\"text-align: center; margin: 0cm 0cm 0pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt\\\\\">嘉鱼县</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\">地方税费征收保障</span><span style=\\\\\"font-family: 黑体; font-size: 16pt\\\\\">工作目标管理考核办法<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 16pt\\\\\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">为加强地方税收管理，保障财政收入持续稳定增长，特制定本办法。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">一、考核原则<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）实事求是、客观公正原则。坚持以事实为依据，客观公正地反映各单位协税护税工作实绩。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（二）明确职责、公开透明原则。根据各单位在地方税费征收保障工作中承担的责任和义务，公开进行考核，公布考核结果。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（三）奖惩结合、激励为主原则。根据考核结果实施奖惩，有效调动有关单位的工作积极性。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 29.4pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.1\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">二、考核机构<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">地方税费征收保障考核工作，在县地方税费征收保障工作领导小组的指导下，由县地方税费征收保障工作领导小组办公室按季组织考核，并通报考核结果。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 29.4pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.1\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">三、考核对象</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt; mso-hansi-font-family: 宋体; mso-bidi-font-family: 宋体\\\\\"></span><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">发改局、住建局、财政局、国税局、地税局、工商局、物价局、经信局、交通运输局、水利局、科技局、民政局、教育局、人社局、国土资源局、公安局、农业局、供电公司、质监局、统计局、环保局、卫生局、招商局、招投标局、县人民银行、嘉鱼经济开发区、文体新局、残联、规划执法局等单位。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 29.4pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.1\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">四、考核内容<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">地方税费征收保障工作考核实行百分制。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 21pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 1.5\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">（一）责任落实（<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>分）<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">认真落实地方税费征收保障责任，建立组织机构，明确专（兼）职工作人员，落实各项工作措施的得<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">20</span>分。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">1</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、有领导班子成员分管的得<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>分，没有分管领导的扣<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>分。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">2</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、建立组织机构，明确专（兼）职工作人员的得<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">3</span>分，否则不得分。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">3</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、明确<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">1</span>名信息员负责收集本单位涉税信息的得<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">4</span>分，否则不得。<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p>\r\n<p class=\\\\\"MsoNormal\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; text-indent: 28pt; margin: 15.6pt 0cm; mso-para-margin-top: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-right: 0cm; mso-para-margin-bottom: 1.0gd; mso-para-margin-left: 0cm; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0\\\\\"><span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\" style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">4</span><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-family: 仿宋_GB2312; font-size: 14pt\\\\\">、按规定参加县地方税费征收保障工作相关会议或培训活动的得<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">10</span>分，每缺席一人次扣<span lang=\\\\\"EN-US\\\\\">2</span>分。